f3203de","tid":1503632,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:55:50.000Z","msg":"唇寒齒亡？識唔識中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf6bf657a74f9ea5b453056883c82babd669525","tid":1503632,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:01:53.000Z","msg":"1. 支共官方指大飢荒只係去到1961，話1963仲係飢荒，想顛覆國家?<br />\n<br />\n2. 60年代香港本土糧食產量係夠供應香港過半人口嘅。<br />\n尤其係主要糧食稻米，以前係本地米，慢慢轉向東南亞米，支那米一直都係少數。<br />\n<br />\n3. 東江水係生意，而且支那賺到笑"},{"pid":"6495080db94519c1b9408b1d841a878354e4d307","tid":1503632,"uid":26942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:05:54.000Z","msg":"拆唔拆都係藍 依家全球化世界 有錢 無話無邊個唔得 新加波就係好例子"},{"pid":"4325155a848375a7f3cb04310d97fd5cd4e49d20","tid":1503632,"uid":129848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"咁嘅大話都信嘅話係唔係都冇救啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca33c485a6eec8713895e0992e7eb639631202f4","tid":1503632,"uid":138092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"唔care，如果係識得尊重事實嘅有腦人士就唔使做藍絲喇。"},{"pid":"cf15e09ea75defb9e6753538d586cd49aff5f55a","tid":1503632,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca33c485a6eec8713895e0992e7eb639631202f4","tid":1503632,"uid":138092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"唔care，如果係識得尊重事實嘅有腦人士就唔使做藍絲喇。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:06:55.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗，當時響香港經歷過呢啲嘢嘅人， 冇可能會俾佢呃到，但唔想呢啲留言會欺騙到當時不在香港或好細個嘅後生仔"},{"pid":"91686408ced0152289f0732a28920ee25f0a2fdb","tid":1503632,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"上網搵咗一啲資料<br />\n<br />\n1/ 關於香港人口<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1947 年  175萬人<br />\n1950年 201萬人<br />\n1960年 三百萬人<br />\n1963年 342萬人<br />\n<br />\n由香港統計處可以查到<br />\n<br />\n2/ 水資源狀況<br />\n<br />\n1963年發生旱災，全年降雨量只有901毫米<br />\n<br />\n3/ 香港地理環境<br />\n<br />\n缺少天然河流、湖泊<br />\n<br />\n4/ 金融危機<br />\n<br />\n人民網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.people.com.cn/BIG5/jinji/33/174/20010426/452428.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.people.com.cn%2FBIG5%2Fjinji%2F33%2F174%2F20010426%2F452428.html&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUKd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=1a56e926\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.people.com.cn/BIG5/jinji/33/174/20010426/452428.html</a><br />\n<br />\n打大鱷內情十年後曝光  （蘋果日報）<br />\n<a href=\"http://observator-gutentag.blogspot.com/2019/03/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fobservator-gutentag.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F03%2F&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUKd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=f45b88fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://observator-gutentag.blogspot.com/2019/03/</a>"}]}